  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n**Precondition**: u need to install 2 instances of the same build into different folders and its data folder should be empty\r\n\r\n1. given a known seed, recover an account\r\n2. recover the same account on the second instance of the app\r\n3. on both apps, open device settings to check pairing and click Advertise\r\n\r\nAs result, no devices to be paired with until the app is restarted\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1900\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/195113555-1a4ec427-9536-481c-86a7-eb57e25cbf3e.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1900\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/195114111-63d8293e-16ce-4af7-950a-cfeda19c0114.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNOTE: weird warning shown which might not be related to the issue itself\r\n```\r\nWRN 2022-10-11 17:03:10.705+03:00 Error decoding signal                      topics=\"signals-manager\" tid=795324 file=signals_manager.nim:43 err=\"/Users/jenkins/workspace/s-desktop_branches_macos_PR-7738/vendor/nimbus-build-system/vendor/Nim/lib/pure/json.nim(746, 10) `node.kind == JArray` : items() can not iterate a JsonNode of kind JNull\"\r\n```",
